00:16.183 --> 00:18.083
I've been pushed down
these stairs.

00:18.085 --> 00:20.252
Somebody fell down the stairs.

00:21.888 --> 00:23.989
He will get really
aggressive and yell.

00:25.659 --> 00:27.793
This is a child murderer.

00:27.795 --> 00:29.361
That pisses me off.

00:29.363 --> 00:32.931
This is super bad.

00:32.933 --> 00:35.434
This is not a good situation.

00:35.436 --> 00:37.269
My name is Amy Allan.

00:37.271 --> 00:38.904
There's death here.

00:38.906 --> 00:40.639
Don't wanna go down there.

00:40.641 --> 00:41.874
I see dead people.

00:41.876 --> 00:43.976
They hide in the walls
and they watch.

00:43.978 --> 00:46.645
I speak to dead people...

00:46.647 --> 00:49.448
She's definitely
a serial killer.

00:49.450 --> 00:51.283
...and they speak to me.

00:51.285 --> 00:53.419
She's going to torture them.

00:53.421 --> 00:57.222
But there's only one way to know
if my findings are real.

00:57.224 --> 00:59.358
They were all murdered.

00:59.360 --> 01:00.892
I rely on my partner.

01:00.894 --> 01:02.428
I'm Steve Di Schiavi.

01:02.430 --> 01:04.262
I'm a retired New York City
homicide detective.

01:04.263 --> 01:06.965
So is this the only time
you've been physically attacked?

01:06.967 --> 01:10.535
I know every person,
every house has secrets.

01:10.537 --> 01:14.339
There's no question in my mind
that he was talking about Satan.

01:14.341 --> 01:16.041
It's my job to reveal them.

01:16.043 --> 01:17.676
Who do you think
possessed you?

01:17.678 --> 01:19.845
But Steve and I
never speak...

01:19.847 --> 01:21.880
We never communicate
during an investigation.

01:21.882 --> 01:23.148
...until the very end.

01:23.150 --> 01:24.750
Well, you're not gonna want
to see this.

01:24.752 --> 01:26.852
When we uncover if it's safe
for you to stay...

01:26.854 --> 01:28.353
<i>Hell,</i> no.

