can influence her findings,

02:21.809 --> 02:25.144
so it's important I cover
or remove them all.

02:25.146 --> 02:26.945
When I'm finished,
the location will be ready

02:26.947 --> 02:29.114
for tonight's walk.

02:39.193 --> 02:43.362
The first thing that I got
was...

02:43.364 --> 02:47.566
in huge, like, bold letters...

02:47.568 --> 02:50.469
was the word "sad."

02:54.775 --> 02:58.176
First thing I'm getting
is a woman upstairs,

02:58.178 --> 02:59.845
and she wants me to
come up there

02:59.847 --> 03:02.881
because she's saying that
the children are in danger.

03:04.384 --> 03:07.319
She's freaking out.
She's freaking out.

03:15.663 --> 03:17.062
So, Carrie, when we spoke
on the phone,

03:17.064 --> 03:18.697
you sounded pretty upset.

03:18.699 --> 03:19.931
What's happening?

03:19.933 --> 03:22.134
This place is tearing
my family apart,

03:22.136 --> 03:25.070
mentally, physically,

03:25.072 --> 03:27.572
and emotionally.

03:27.574 --> 03:29.508
And then my children...

03:29.510 --> 03:32.444
my children are scared
to even be here.

03:32.446 --> 03:34.479
How long have you actually
lived in the house?

03:34.481 --> 03:37.949
I have lived here
a little over 21/2 years.

03:37.951 --> 03:39.250
Okay.

03:39.252 --> 03:42.420
And when my husband's
grandparents passed away,

03:42.422 --> 03:43.622
we got the home.

03:43.624 --> 03:46.491
Did his grandparents
pass away in the house?

03:46.493 --> 03:47.525
No, they did not.

03:47.527 --> 03:50.696
They passed away
in a nursing home.

03:50.698 --> 03:53.598
Who exactly
lives in the house?

03:53.600 --> 03:56.901
You got myself,
my husband, Chad.

03:56.903 --> 04:00.539
You got my daughter Ariana,
who is 11.

04:00.541 --> 04:03.574
You got my daughter Victoria,
who is 10,

04:03.576 --> 04:05.777
my daughter Layla,
who is 5.

04:05.779 --> 04:08.112
and then Gabrielle,
who is 3.

04:08.114 --> 04:09.214
So, Carrie, do me a favor.

04:09.216 --> 04:11.717
Give me a list of things
that are happening.

04:11.719 --> 04:15.153
We're hearing voices,
footsteps.

04:15.155 --> 04:16.853
Our health is declining.

04:16.856 --> 04:18.923
We're getting
physical attacks.

04:18.926 --> 04:20.926
I'm seeing shadow figures.

04:20.928 --> 04:24.730
Is everybody being affected,
or is it just specific people?

04:24.732 --> 04:27.165
It's affecting my husband.

04:27.167 --> 04:28.867
We were happily married.

04:28.869 --> 04:32.771
Recently, he started becoming
really depressed.

04:32.773 --> 04:36.207
What makes you so convinced
that his changes

04:36.209 --> 04:38.142
have anything to do
with the paranormal?

04:38.144 --> 04:42.280
Because before we moved
into here, we never fought.

04:42.282 --> 04:45.550
And then his depression
started kicking in.

04:45.552 --> 04:46.984
Once second, he's happy,

04:46.986 --> 04:49.755
and the next minute, he's
snapping and yelling at people,

04:49.757 --> 04:53.225
trying to accuse me of doing
something wrong that I'm not.

04:53.227 --> 04:54.626
Okay.

04:54.628 --> 04:57.028
I think there's something here
that is attached to him.

04:57.030 --> 04:58.896
It won't let him go.

04:58.898 --> 05:00.765
Whatever is going on can't
be good for the marriage.

05:00.767 --> 05:02.801
No.
This could be the end of it

05:02.803 --> 05:05.870
if we don't figure out
what is going on.

05:05.872 --> 05:07.772
You know, it's heartbreaking
to listen to you talk.

05:07.774 --> 05:09.508
And, you know, one of
the reasons I took the case

05:09.510 --> 05:11.242
is 'cause of the kids.

05:11.244 --> 05:12.744
But it sounds like
you're the one

05:12.746 --> 05:14.579
that really needs
the help here.

05:14.581 --> 05:15.781
Yeah.

05:17.350 --> 05:19.618
I ain't got no one
to turn to.

05:19.620 --> 05:22.720
And I need help.

05:22.722 --> 05:24.623
I want this fixed.

05:24.625 --> 05:26.658
I want to be better.

05:30.798 --> 05:33.799
There's a male,
and he's over to my right.

05:33.801 --> 05:35.133
He's dead.

05:35.135 --> 05:38.503
He's like,
"Lies! They're saying lies!"

05:38.505 --> 05:43.275
His energy is <i> crazy</i> strong.

05:43.277 --> 05:45.109
I'm getting violence here.

05:45.111 --> 05:46.411
"Aah!"

05:48.382 --> 05:52.150
Like, I'm hearing a living man
yelling,

05:52.152 --> 05:55.153
screaming, crying,
wanting to kill.

05:56.957 --> 06:00.892
Something is influencing males

06:00.894 --> 06:02.594
to be violent.

06:09.036 --> 06:10.101
So you brought me up here.

06:10.103 --> 06:11.969
I'm assuming you've
had experiences.

06:11.971 --> 06:15.574
Yeah. I have been seeing
a small shadow.

06:15.576 --> 06:17.175
Well, how tall
are we talking about?

06:17.177 --> 06:19.644
Probably about
my daughter Layla's size.

06:19.646 --> 06:21.579
Could that shadow
have been Layla?

06:21.581 --> 06:24.382
No, because when
I come up here and check,

06:24.384 --> 06:25.717
either Layla is sleeping

06:25.719 --> 06:28.586
or she's gone at her grandma's
for the weekend.

06:28.588 --> 06:31.790
Okay. Have you seen any other
shadows besides that one?

06:31.792 --> 06:35.059
Yeah. I've seen one that is
a lot taller than that one.

06:35.061 --> 06:36.461
How often you seeing these?

06:36.463 --> 06:37.696
- Daily.
- Daily?

06:37.698 --> 06:39.997
- Yeah.
- Anything else?

06:39.999 --> 06:43.935
I've been pushed down
these stairs.

06:43.937 --> 06:46.104
I actually broke my foot.

06:46.106 --> 06:48.005
You're lucky you
didn't get killed.
Yeah.

06:48.007 --> 06:50.708
How hard did you get pushed?
Show me. Give me a shove.

06:50.710 --> 06:52.077
- Like that.
- All right.

06:52.079 --> 06:55.080
So you know how lucky
you are, right?
Yes.

06:55.082 --> 06:56.748
I mean, you could have got
knocked unconscious,

06:56.750 --> 06:59.151
broke your neck, anything.
- Yeah.

07:01.621 --> 07:04.088
The dead guy,
he knows that he can

07:04.090 --> 07:06.424
take his energy and throw it.

07:06.426 --> 07:11.696
Living people, I'd think,
be prone to falls here.

07:11.698 --> 07:15.367
When he puts out
his energy like this,

07:15.369 --> 07:17.969
it definitely affects
your equilibrium.

07:17.971 --> 07:19.905
People would feel like
their feet

07:19.907 --> 07:22.540
are coming out from under them.

07:22.542 --> 07:25.710
Somebody fell down the stairs.

07:27.247 --> 07:30.815
If he is able to...

07:30.817 --> 07:34.051
throw somebody down the stairs,

07:34.053 --> 07:36.021
that's not good.

07:41.528 --> 07:43.261
Okay, what's going on
up here?

07:43.263 --> 07:47.199
Well, I have been touched
inappropriately in the bathroom.

07:47.201 --> 07:48.399
Mind me asking what happened?

07:48.401 --> 07:50.034
I thought it was Chad.

07:50.036 --> 07:52.803
It felt like somebody
just grabbed my rear.

07:52.805 --> 07:55.006
I jumped out the shower
pretty quick.

07:55.008 --> 07:57.208
And I went and yelled
at Chad, you know,

07:57.210 --> 07:58.877
"Why the hell
did you do that?"

07:58.879 --> 08:01.813
And I look in here, and he's in
the bedroom, sitting on the bed.

08:01.815 --> 08:03.781
Now did that ever
happen again?

08:03.783 --> 08:05.283
Yeah.

08:05.285 --> 08:07.351
It happened one more time when
I was laying in bed at night.

08:07.353 --> 08:08.286
Same touch?

08:08.288 --> 08:11.188
Like, the inside of my legs.

08:11.190 --> 08:13.758
- Okay. And...
- Chad was sleeping.

08:13.760 --> 08:14.959
Okay. Not that
I'm not believing you,

08:14.961 --> 08:16.627
but, I mean,
you have a dog right here.

08:16.629 --> 08:19.030
You sure she or he
didn't just...

08:19.032 --> 08:20.365
No, 'cause at the time,

08:20.367 --> 08:22.767
she was sleeping
down in the living room.

08:22.769 --> 08:24.168
All right.
What else is going on?

08:24.170 --> 08:27.038
My declining health.

08:27.040 --> 08:30.709
I have had
four partial hysterectomies.

08:30.711 --> 08:33.979
I have had
my appendix taken out.

08:33.981 --> 08:35.712
I've had my gall bladder
taken out.

08:35.715 --> 08:37.582
Whenever I'm getting anxiety,

08:37.583 --> 08:40.784
it makes me feel like
I'm having a heart attack.

08:40.787 --> 08:42.653
Well, living here and telling me
what you're going through --

08:42.655 --> 08:43.855
getting pushed down
a flight of stairs,

08:43.857 --> 08:46.190
somebody grabbing your...
in the shower,

08:46.192 --> 08:48.326
I mean, I'd be
a little anxious, too.

08:48.328 --> 08:49.861
This house is killing me.

08:49.863 --> 08:51.563
What are you hoping
we can do for you?

08:51.565 --> 08:54.933
I am hoping that my relationship
with my husband

08:54.935 --> 08:58.203
goes back to normal
like it was.

08:58.205 --> 09:02.840
I'm worried that we're gonna
end up going our separate ways.

09:02.842 --> 09:06.545
I want to be the way we were
2 years ago,

09:06.547 --> 09:07.946
happily married.

09:09.649 --> 09:12.750
I think if living people
are having the experience,

09:12.752 --> 09:15.954
I could kind of see them

09:15.956 --> 09:19.624
possibly thinking
they were being grabbed.

09:19.626 --> 09:24.229
And I got a bad pain in my head,
really, really bad.

09:24.231 --> 09:26.497
Ooh, ooh.

09:26.499 --> 09:28.300
Wow. What did he do?

09:28.302 --> 09:29.701
Ooh.

09:29.703 --> 09:32.037
I'm nauseous and dizzy.

09:32.039 --> 09:34.839
The left side of my head
is wicked bad.

09:37.310 --> 09:38.510
Mnh.

09:38.512 --> 09:41.179
I think this is associated
with the dead male.

09:41.181 --> 09:44.516
He's yelling, "You stupid!
