It grabbed me
just like that. Like, hard.

10:36.303 --> 10:37.469
Really?

10:37.471 --> 10:39.170
What about you, Victoria?
What's going on?

10:39.172 --> 10:42.073
I have bad nightmares.

10:42.075 --> 10:44.109
Okay.
Do you remember them?

10:44.111 --> 10:48.012
All I remember about them,
my mom had to,

10:48.014 --> 10:50.481
and my stepdad,
had to wake me up.

10:50.483 --> 10:52.951
Ariana, anything else that
you've seen that scared you?

10:52.953 --> 10:55.954
I have seen a really tall
shadow man

10:55.956 --> 11:00.091
with, like, a top hat
and facial hair.

11:00.093 --> 11:02.360
Okay. Now where did you
see that?

11:02.362 --> 11:04.929
It is mainly
in the hallways.

11:07.100 --> 11:09.167
Are you sure it wasn't
your stepdad?

11:09.169 --> 11:10.802
Yes.

11:10.804 --> 11:14.305
So, guys, I was talking
to Mom and Dad.

11:14.307 --> 11:17.108
I'm curious. Have you seen
a change in either one of them?

11:17.110 --> 11:19.310
Chad. He's been
getting really mean.

11:19.312 --> 11:23.381
When your stepdad Chad
gets angry, what happens?

11:23.383 --> 11:27.919
