yelling from...

11:49.476 --> 11:51.676
I guess this room.

11:51.678 --> 11:57.782
There is a living male, like,
acting out, like, just snapping.

11:59.753 --> 12:03.288
Like a complete change.

12:09.863 --> 12:11.296
So, Chad, I was talking
to your wife.

12:11.298 --> 12:13.832
In her opinion,
since you guys moved in here,

12:13.834 --> 12:15.900
your personality changed.

12:15.902 --> 12:18.235
- Yeah. I agree with her.
