How you feeling?

12:22.976 --> 12:25.243
Angry, very angry.

12:25.245 --> 12:26.978
It comes to the point
where I feel like

12:26.980 --> 12:28.746
I want to rip walls apart,

12:28.748 --> 12:31.516
tear 'em down,
anyone in my way.

12:31.518 --> 12:33.317
Your wife told me
about her experiences.

12:33.319 --> 12:35.253
How about you?
Any experiences?

12:35.255 --> 12:37.088
I got out of the shower
one time.

12:37.090 --> 12:41.392
Me and my wife, when we seen
on the mirror, from the fog,

12:41.394 --> 12:43.127
