on it.

12:43.129 --> 12:46.931
So I ran down the hallway
and woke the girls up

12:46.933 --> 12:48.166
out of a dead sleep.

12:48.168 --> 12:49.868
I was furious.
I told them,

12:49.870 --> 12:51.402
"Are you guys playing games?"
- Right.

12:51.404 --> 12:53.671
They almost started crying,
"It wasn't us.

12:53.673 --> 12:55.206
It wasn't us.
It wasn't us."

12:55.208 --> 12:56.975
You're pretty convinced
the kids didn't do it.

12:56.977 --> 12:59.944
I'm 100%.

12:59.946 --> 13:01.479
Okay. Has anything else
happened?

13:01.481 --> 13:04.215
When I'm sleeping, I feel
like something's choking me

13:04.217 --> 13:05.550
and sitting on my chest.

13:05.552 --> 13:06.717
Wait. Describe
the feeling to me.

13:06.719 --> 13:08.686
It feels like you
can't breathe or...

13:08.688 --> 13:11.289
Sit up and...
