13:11.291 --> 13:13.925
I thought it was trying
to kill me, suffocate me.

13:13.927 --> 13:15.359
Couldn't get no air.

13:15.361 --> 13:17.728
Now do you suffer from any
asthma or anything like that?

13:17.730 --> 13:18.930
No.

13:18.932 --> 13:20.165
Now how were you reacting
when this happened?

13:20.167 --> 13:21.499
Furious.

13:21.501 --> 13:23.000
- Okay.
