He's showing people
people sitting, sitting here,

14:10.750 --> 14:15.553
and he's showing me him
smacking them upside the head.

14:15.555 --> 14:18.422
You know? Like, just whap.

14:18.424 --> 14:19.824
All of a sudden,
they start feeling

14:19.826 --> 14:23.127
like they're getting smacked on
the, you know, like...

