So from what Carrie told me,

14:26.866 --> 14:28.833
you inherited this house
from your grandparents.

14:28.835 --> 14:29.968
Correct.

14:29.970 --> 14:31.769
How far apart
did they pass away?

14:31.771 --> 14:33.704
A year.

14:33.706 --> 14:35.106
I see you're looking over here.
Is this them?

14:35.108 --> 14:36.574
That is them. Yes, it is.

14:36.576 --> 14:39.010
What did they die from?

14:39.012 --> 14:41.579
Actually, my grandmother
had a brain tumor.

14:41.581 --> 14:43.447
And your grandfather?

14:43.449 --> 14:45.950
He died from gangrene,
pretty much.

14:45.952 --> 14:48.519
And he just kind of rotted
from his feet up.

14:48.521 --> 14:49.853
What kind of guy was he?

14:49.855 --> 14:52.556
He's a good guy,
but he didn't like women.

14:52.558 --> 14:54.858
He had
a very super bad temper.

14:54.860 --> 14:56.127
Any abuse?

14:56.129 --> 14:58.529
Yeah, I've never seen him
ever do physical abuse

14:58.531 --> 15:00.398
but a lot of mental.

15:00.400 --> 15:03.201
Do you think
your grandparents are here?

15:03.203 --> 15:05.536
Yeah. I do.

